aa(lp161
VAnd then I went away for four months
p162
aVand there was going to be groundbreaking.
p163
aVAnd I came back and, lo and behold, the little model I'd left behind
p164
aVhad been built ten times bigger for public display on site
p165
aVand ... the bridge was built!
p166
aV(Laughter)
p167
aVWithin the working drawings!
p168
aVAnd half a million people gathered for the celebrations;
p169
aVyou can see them on the site itself as the foundations are beginning.
