aa(lp173
VBack to Yad Vashem three years ago. After all this episode began,
p174
aVYad Vashem decided to rebuild completely the historic museum
p175
aVbecause now Washington was built \u2014 the Holocaust Museum in Washington \u2014
p176
aVand that museum is so much more comprehensive in terms of information.
p177
aVAnd Yad Vashem needs to deal with three million visitors a year at this point.
p178
aVThey said, "Let's rebuild the museum."
p179
aVBut of course, the Sikhs might give you a job on a platter \u2014 the Jews make it hard:
p180
aVinternational competition, phase one, phase two, phase three.
p181
aV(Laughter)
